Expand the range of values for density plot

expand_range.Rd

Expand the range of values for density plot

Usage 

expand_range(
  x,
  expand_left_side = 0.1,
  expand_right_side = 0.2,
  type = c("relative", "absolute")
)

Arguments

x

numeric vector

expand_left_side

Fraction to expand on left hand side

expand_right_side

Fraction to expand on right hand side

Value

Vector of 2 values
